These are Puzzles for 3x3 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 3x3-Level-2-1::.
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: july, october, june
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: thriller, sports, satire
City: san-francisco, boston, liverpool
1. the person who's birthday is in june is the person traveling to liverpool##1
2. the person watching thriller movies is between the person who's birthday is in june and the person who's birthday is in july##2
3. the person traveling to boston is on the right of the person watching satire movies##1
4. the person watching thriller movies is on the left of the person who's birthday is in july##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1     |    2    |   3   |
| Birthday        | june | october | july |
| Movie-Genre         | satire    | thriller     | sports  |
| City   | liverpool     | boston     | san-francisco  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x3-Level-2-2::.
3 different pets are kept: mouse, lizard, fish
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: may, september, april
City: edinburgh, london, san-francisco
1. the person who's birthday is in september is the person traveling to edinburgh##1
2. the owner of the fish is on the right of the person who's birthday is in april##1
3. the owner of the lizard is between the person traveling to san-francisco and the owner of the mouse##2

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1    |      2      |        3        |
| Pet   | mouse    | lizard       | fish             |
| Birthday      | september  | april | may      |
| City        | edinburgh | london    | san-francisco |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x3-Level-2-3::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: lemonade, almond-milk, milk
The people use 3 different means of transport: bus, tram, train
The people have 3 different hobbies: baking, sudoku, singing
1. the person driving the bus is on the left of the person drinking almond-milk##1
2. the person driving the bus is on the left of the person driving the train##1
3. the person driving the bus is the person who's hobby is baking##1
4. the person who's hobby is baking is between the person drinking milk and the person who's hobby is singing##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |      3      |
| Beverage           | milk    | lemonade   | almond-milk |
| Transport   | tram | bus   | train         |
| Hobby         | sudoku     | baking | singing     |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x3-Level-2-4::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: hiking, cooking, woodworking
House: cottage, art-deco, craftsman
3 different games are played: mah-jongg, bridge, whist
1. the person playing bridge is on the far right##1
2. the cottage house is on the left of the person playing whist##1
3. the person playing whist is between the cottage house and the person who's hobby is hiking##2
4. the art-deco house is on the right of the person who's hobby is cooking##1
5. the art-deco house is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |   2   |     3     |
| Hobby   | woodworking    | cooking  | hiking     |
| House   | cottage       | craftsman   | art-deco       |
| Game     | mah-jongg | whist | bridge |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x3-Level-2-5::.
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: rowing, golf, basketball
3 different games are played: monopoly, poker, chess
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: daisy, iris, daffodil
1. the person who's sport is golf is the person playing monopoly##1
2. the person playing monopoly is on the right of the person who growsdaisy##1
3. the person who's sport is rowing is the person who growsiris##1
4. the person playing monopoly is between the person playing poker and the person who's sport is rowing##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |   2    |    3    |
| Sport   | basketball | golf   | rowing   |
| Game           | poker   | monopoly | chess     |
| Flower     | daisy   | daffodil    | iris |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x3-Level-2-6::.
3 different pets are kept: goldfish, chinchilla, cat
City: nizza, london, miami
There 3 different types of food: mango, papaya, raspberry
1. the person traveling to miami is on the left of the owner of the cat##1
2. the person eating raspberry is on the left of the owner of the goldfish##1
3. the person eating papaya is between the person traveling to london and the person eating raspberry##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |    3    |
| Pet         | chinchilla   | goldfish | cat |
| City   | nizza | miami      | london  |
| Food   | raspberry      | papaya   | mango |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x3-Level-2-7::.
3 different pets are kept: mouse, goldfish, guinea-pig
There are 3 different nationalities: german, chinese, american
There 3 different types of food: papaya, cranberry, raspberry
1. the owner of the mouse is on the right of the american##1
2. the person eating raspberry is on the left of the person eating papaya##1
3. the owner of the guinea-pig is between the person eating papaya and the german##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |      3      |
| Pet   | goldfish    | guinea-pig    | mouse |
| Nationality         | german   | american     | chinese     |
| Food     | cranberry | raspberry | papaya     |

