.:: Puzzle 3x3-Level-2-8::.
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: musical, crime, adventure
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: april, march, december
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: montecristo, alhambra, dunhill
1. the person watching adventure movies is on the left of the person who's birthday is in december##1
2. the alhambra-smoker is on the left of the dunhill-smoker##1
3. the person watching musical movies is between the person who's birthday is in march and the montecristo-smoker##2
4. the person who's birthday is in march is the person watching adventure movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |     2      |     3      |
| Movie-Genre         | adventure | musical | crime  |
| Birthday   | march        | december        | april |
| Cigar         | alhambra         | dunhill    | montecristo   |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x3-Level-2-9::.
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: oliveros, chaman, dannemann
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: sailing, cycling, rugby
There are 3 different favourite beverages: cola, water, almond-milk
1. the chaman-smoker is between the person who's sport is rugby and the oliveros-smoker##2
2. the person drinking almond-milk is between the person drinking cola and the oliveros-smoker##2
3. the person who's sport is sailing is in the middle##1
4. the person who's sport is rugby is on the left of the person who's sport is sailing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1    |     2      |    3     |
| Cigar         | dannemann | chaman  | oliveros  |
| Sport         | rugby    | sailing | cycling |
| Beverage   | cola    | almond-milk       | water  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x3-Level-2-10::.
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: begonia, orchid, daisy
House: townhouse, colonial, wooden
The people have 3 different hobbies: drawing, woodworking, magic-tricks
1. the townhouse house is the person who's hobby is drawing##1
2. the person who growsbegonia is between the colonial house and the person who growsdaisy##2
3. the person who's hobby is drawing is on the right of the person who's hobby is woodworking##1
4. the wooden house is on the left of the person who growsdaisy##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |       2       |    3     |
| Flower   | orchid       | begonia         | daisy      |
| House   | colonial | wooden       | townhouse |
| Hobby         | magic-tricks     | woodworking | drawing |

