.:: Puzzle 3x3-Level-2-11::.
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: romance, martial-arts, horror
There are 3 different nationalities: thai, russian, chinese
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: poppy, aconite, orchid
1. the person watching romance movies is on the left of the chinese##1
2. the russian is on the left of the person who growsaconite##1
3. the thai is on the right of the person watching horror movies##1
4. the thai is between the person watching horror movies and the person who growsorchid##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |       2       |       3       |
| Movie-Genre         | horror | romance  | martial-arts |
| Nationality   | russian      | thai       | chinese          |
| Flower         | poppy  | aconite | orchid        |

