.:: Puzzle 3x3-Level-2-12::.
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: chaman, bolivar, montecristo
There 3 different types of food: lemon, lettuce, grapes
There are 3 different favourite beverages: lemonade, sprite, milk
1. the person drinking lemonade is on the right of the person eating grapes##1
2. the chaman-smoker is in the middle##1
3. the chaman-smoker is on the left of the montecristo-smoker##1
4. the person eating lemon is between the person eating grapes and the person drinking milk##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2     |      3       |
| Cigar           | bolivar   | chaman | montecristo |
| Food   | grapes | lemon     | lettuce       |
| Beverage   | sprite    | lemonade | milk       |

