.:: Puzzle 3x3-Level-2-13::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: chess, drawing, reading
There are 3 different favourite beverages: water, tea, juice
City: marseilles, prague, nizza
1. the person drinking juice is between the person traveling to nizza and the person who's hobby is reading##2
2. the person traveling to marseilles is on the right of the person who's hobby is drawing##1
3. the person traveling to prague is on the right of the person traveling to marseilles##1
4. the person who's hobby is chess is on the left of the person drinking water##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2     |       3       |
| Hobby          | drawing      | chess | reading     |
| Beverage   | tea | juice  | water     |
| City         | nizza  | marseilles | prague |

