.:: Puzzle 3x3-Level-2-14::.
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: tennis, biathlon, weightlifting
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: cain, vegafina, dunhill
There are 3 different favourite beverages: juice, coffee, mirinda
1. the person who's sport is weightlifting is on the left of the person who's sport is biathlon##1
2. the vegafina-smoker is the person who's sport is biathlon##1
3. the person drinking mirinda is on the right of the vegafina-smoker##1
4. the person drinking coffee is between the dunhill-smoker and the person who's sport is weightlifting##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1   |      2      |     3      |
| Sport   | weightlifting | biathlon | tennis   |
| Cigar           | cain  | vegafina        | dunhill     |
| Beverage     | juice  | coffee   | mirinda |

