.:: Puzzle 3x3-Level-2-15::.
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: february, august, october
There are 3 different nationalities: brazilian, polish, canadian
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: rowing, lacrosse, climbing
1. the person who's birthday is in october is on the left of the brazilian##1
2. the person who's sport is lacrosse is between the canadian and the person who's birthday is in february##2
3. the polish is between the person who's sport is rowing and the person who's birthday is in august##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |  2   |    3    |
| Birthday      | august    | october  | february |
| Nationality          | canadian | polish | brazilian |
| Sport   | climbing      | lacrosse | rowing   |

