2. the person traveling to miami is on the right of the person who growsamaryllis##1
3. the person who growsrose is between the person traveling to colone and the person who growsdaisy##2

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1     |    2     |       3        |
| Transport   | snowmobile | roller   | helicopter        |
| Flower     | amaryllis   | rose    | daisy |
| City   | colone     | miami | san-francisco     |

