.:: Puzzle 3x3-Level-2-17::.
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: parkour, cricket, golf
3 different pets are kept: ferret, guinea-pig, goat
The people use 3 different means of transport: snowmobile, ship, roller
1. the person who's sport is parkour is on the left of the person who's sport is cricket##1
2. the person driving the roller is between the person who's sport is parkour and the owner of the ferret##2
3. the person who's sport is golf is on the right of the owner of the guinea-pig##1
4. the owner of the ferret is the person driving the snowmobile##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2     |     3     |
| Sport      | parkour | cricket | golf     |
| Pet           | goat      | guinea-pig | ferret     |
| Transport   | ship       | roller      | snowmobile |

