.:: Puzzle 3x3-Level-2-18::.
3 different pets are kept: hamster, mouse, rat
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: weightlifting, sailing, swimming
There are 3 different favourite beverages: milk, mirinda, tea
1. the owner of the rat is the person drinking mirinda##1
2. the person who's sport is sailing is on the far left##1
3. the person who's sport is swimming is on the right of the owner of the hamster##1
4. the person who's sport is swimming is between the person drinking tea and the person drinking mirinda##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2    |     3     |
| Pet         | hamster | mouse | rat |
| Sport           | sailing   | swimming   | weightlifting |
| Beverage   | tea     | milk | mirinda   |

