.:: Puzzle 3x3-Level-2-19::.
There are 3 different favourite colors: red, lavender, aquamarine
3 different games are played: bridge, whist, snooker
3 different pets are kept: fish, goldfish, turtle
1. the person who likes lavender is between the person playing snooker and the owner of the turtle##2
2. the person who likes aquamarine is the owner of the goldfish##1
3. the owner of the fish is the person who likes lavender##1
4. the person playing whist is on the left of the owner of the turtle##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |       1       |     2     |      3       |
| Color   | aquamarine | lavender      | red  |
| Game      | snooker   | whist   | bridge      |
| Pet        | goldfish     | fish | turtle |

