.:: Puzzle 3x3-Level-2-20::.
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: aristoff, siglo, bolivar
The people have 3 different jobs:  scientist, firefighter, videographer
3 different games are played: canasta, go, poker
1. the person playing poker is on the left of the scientist##1
2. the videographer is on the left of the person playing canasta##1
3. the siglo-smoker is on the right of the person playing canasta##1
4. the aristoff-smoker is between the firefighter and the bolivar-smoker##2

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1     |     2      |    3    |
| Cigar    | bolivar     | aristoff     | siglo |
| Job       | videographer | scientist | firefighter |
| Game   | poker     | canasta       | go    |

 